{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"511ce2f628","title":"黄碾公社“四清”结束后出现两方面的问题","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5b54927503","index":0,"year":1964,"month":5,"day":8,"articleId":"511ce2f628"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"e0650d6015","name":"冯东书"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4849b1ece4","type":"title","text":"黄碾公社“四清”结束后出现两方面的问题","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"511ce2f628"},{"id":"c884c28d47","type":"authors","text":"冯东书","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"511ce2f628"},{"id":"649575718c","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社太原讯    山西长治市黄碾公社“四清”结束不久就出现了以下两方面的问题：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"511ce2f628"},{"id":"f37fd5152f","type":"paragraph","text":"第一、刮起了翻案风。全公社犯错误的四百多个干部、职工中，有百分之十的人想翻案（不属应订正的性质），其中百分之二点五的人已经公开翻案。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"511ce2f628"},{"id":"0783f19bca","type":"paragraph","text":"与翻案风相联系的是，一部分下台干部，资产阶级思想阴魂不散，在下面为非作歹，和新上台干部闹摩擦。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"511ce2f628"},{"id":"b1c5b29499","type":"paragraph","text":"第二、新上台的干部又开始了“四不清”。四个月中，小常、黄研、安居等四个大队，又发现新“四不清”事件十四起。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"511ce2f628"},{"id":"8bc7be5f76","type":"paragraph","text":"黄碾公社针对这种情况，依靠贫、下中农开展了反翻案斗争和反新“四不清”斗争。（冯东书）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"511ce2f628"},{"id":"1ea2095b9b","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据1964年5月8日新华社《内部参考》。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"511ce2f628"}],"page":{"id":"fbba45e452","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"511ce2f628","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}